# Next.js OpenAI Application

This is the main cursor rule file for the Next.js OpenAI application. It provides an overview of the project and references to more specific rule files.

## Project Overview

This is a Next.js application that integrates with various AI providers including OpenAI, Anthropic, and others. The project uses the AI SDK for React and follows the App Router pattern.

